みいちゃんみいちゃん、なぜ<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">泣</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">な</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>く、<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">青</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">あお</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>い<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">空</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">そら</span><span type="rp">）</span></span><span type="ruby"><span type="rb">見</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">み</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>て<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">泣</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">な</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>くんだ。<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">青</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">あお</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>い<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">空</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">そら</span><span type="rp">）</span></span><span type="ruby"><span type="rb">見</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">み</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>てなぜ<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">泣</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">な</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>く、<lb />
つばめの<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">行方</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ゆくえ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>が<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">悲</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">かな</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>しくて、<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">母</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">かか</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>を<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">思</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">おも</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>うて<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">泣</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">な</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>くんだ。<lb />
